short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AI-powered website summarization generates a concise and brief digest of the content found on a given website.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This AI-powered productivity app makes it easy for you to generate summaries of any online content you come across, helping you save time and be more productive. With our unique voice assistant feature, which includes Text-to-Speech Speaker functionality, you can even listen to content. This saves time and allows you to take your eyes off the screen. Whether you prefer to use our browser extension or web application, this tool is designed to help busy professionals optimize their productivity. Try our app now and experience the benefits of AI!

Features and Benefits 
- Website Summary
- Text-to-Speech
- Time Savings
- Multi Task
